# 📺 YouTube Video Summarizer

This project is a **YouTube Video Summarizer** built using **Python** and external **APIs**. It takes the URL of a YouTube video, extracts its transcript (if available), and generates a **concise and easy-to-understand summary**, saving you time and helping you grasp the video content quickly.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔗 Accepts YouTube video URLs as input
- 🧠 Automatically extracts transcript using APIs
- ✂️ Summarizes long video content into short, readable points
- ⏱️ Saves time by avoiding full video watch
- 💬 Clean, text-based summary output

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Python 
- **YouTube Transcript API**
- **Text Summarization Libraries** Huggingface transformers
